item.title: Notes from rstudio::conf(2020L)
item.author: danielrlabar@gmail.com (Dan LaBar)
item.description: Day 3 sessions (2020-01-29) Open Source Software for Data Science Data, Visualization, and Designing with AI Deploying End-to-End Data Science with Shiny, Plumber, and Pins We’re hitting R a million times a day so we made a talk about it Practical Plumber Patterns Azure Pipelines and Github Actions Accelerating Analytics with Apache Arrow Updates on Spark MLFlow, and the broader ML ecosystem What’s new in Tensorflow for R?
